<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 15:23:01 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>尽管特朗普大力推动加密货币资本，但比特币仍跌破 73,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-28/bitcoin-falls-below-73-000-despite-trump-s-crypto-capital-push</link><description>尽管唐纳德·特朗普再次推动《清晰法案》，但比特币仍短暂跌破 73,000 美元，这表明华盛顿支持加密货币的消息正在失去推动数字资产上涨的能力。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/isDbNUm3RRmg/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 14:18:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-28/bitcoin-falls-below-73-000-despite-trump-s-crypto-capital-push</guid></item><item><title>由于战争恐慌和 ETF 资金外流，比特币跌至六周低点</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-28/bitcoin-falls-to-five-week-low-amid-war-jitters-etf-outflows</link><description>由于美伊战争的紧张情绪和美国交易所交易基金的资金外流令这一最大的加密货币承压，比特币跌至六周多以来的最低水平。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i0my0ll4FIEQ/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 02:55:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-28/bitcoin-falls-to-five-week-low-amid-war-jitters-etf-outflows</guid></item><item><title>CFTC 撤销 Gemini 支付 500 万美元的和解协议</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-28/cftc-moves-to-undo-settlement-that-had-gemini-paying-5-million</link><description>美国商品期货交易委员会和由亿万富翁 Winklevoss 兄弟领导的 Gemini Trust Co. 希望解除 2025 年的和解协议，该和解协议导致该加密货币交易所同意支付 500 万美元来结束机构诉讼。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ifpmlhLbNGXc/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 03:25:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-28/cftc-moves-to-undo-settlement-that-had-gemini-paying-5-million</guid></item><item><title>国际清算银行和银行构建区块链跨境支付原型</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-27/bis-and-banks-build-blockchain-cross-border-payments-prototype</link><description>国际清算银行和一群合作伙伴将很快开始测试具有实际价值交易的数字跨境支付的新原型。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iPbolxSGToqM/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 May 2026 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-27/bis-and-banks-build-blockchain-cross-border-payments-prototype</guid></item></channel></rss>